examples.en: There are 12 exits in the building.
The crowd proceeded toward the exits.
The tourists piled towards the exits.
The plane's exits are located fore and aft.
People were jamming the exits after the concert.
Doors are provided both for regular use and as emergency exits.
The factory was a death trap with too few exits for the workers to use in case of a fire.
Ramps are needed at exits and entrances for wheelchair users.
